ndependent universe is structurally under-targeted. A_acquire_self confirmed post-enrichment — Phase 5 deep-dive verifies OV65 + live team-page successor + Comptroller status + value-add specificity. DEEP-DIVE DEMOTED A_acquire_self→B_forward: Deep-dive Item 2 (successor verification) blocked: no active company website found in search; only PitchBook + Eagle Pass City Engineering List references. 2 RPLS at firm per TBPELS (Alan D Lindskog 1980 + second 1980s era) suggests succession depth or peer-RPLS. Cannot resolve. Demote to B_forward.', 'AI / ops modernization play on a 46yr-tenured single-RPLS surveying firm in San Antonio:  (1) drone/UAV survey program (~25-40% labor savings on topo + as-built); (2) 3D laser scanning + reality capture for as-built and infrastructure work; (3) online project portal for ALTA / FEMA / boundary client self-service; (4) RTK GPS base station network for sub-cm field productivity; (5) automated CAD/drafting workflow + AI plat-review. Plausible 1.5-2× EBITDA path 18-24 months. Off-market multiple 3-5× EBITDA in current LOW-PE-attention environment; would shift to 5-7× as ETA/search-fund deal-velocity ramps 2026-2027.', 'low', 0.7)
